{"url": "https://book.douban.com/subject/1000029/", "id": "1000029", "title": "中华人民共和国演义", "cover": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s1035214.jpg", "base": "作者:张涛之出版社:作家出版社出版年:1995-05页数:1383定价:57.50装帧:精装ISBN:9787506309332", "intro": "内容提要本书是第一部以中华人民共和国国史为题材的历史演义小说。全书前17回追溯中国共产党领导中国人民创建共和国的历程，后94回描述建国45年间的风风雨雨。作者以史诗般的笔法，以大量的史料，深刻的见地，描绘了历次重大政治运动的来龙去脉，重大政治决策的出台前后，政治领袖们的坎坷命运，各时期风云人物的升降浮沉，共和国的辉煌成就以及她的挫折徘徊……全书结构宏大，内涵丰厚，是广大读者了解共和国全貌的必读之作。作者简介张涛，笔名张涛之，男，1943年生，甘肃省通渭县人。1964年考入中国人民大学历史系，1969年毕业分配到新疆工作，在库尔勒市巴州二中任教。1978年考入中国人民大学研究生院新闻系，1981年毕业并获文学硕士学位，先后任教于中国人民警官大学、中国新闻学院。现为中国新闻史学会副秘书长、教授。主要论著有《中国新闻史》（合著）、 《中华人民共和国新闻史》、《中国报案史话》、《周恩来和新华日报》、《坚持社会主义市场经济条件下新闻改革的正确方向》、《论周恩来领导新华日报的历史经验》、《论皖南新四军之北移路线》等。", "tags": ["历史", "共和国历史", "中华人民共和国演义", "中国", "小说", "历史小说", "中国近代史", "好书"], "score": {"avg": " 7.5 ", "scroe_num": "80", "rating": ["22.5%", "43.8%", "31.3%", "0.0%", "2.5%"]}, "comments": [{"comment_id": "28666266", "nick_name": "芝草", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/witty627/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1555202-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2008-03-18", "content": "<span class=\"short\">文笔实在一般，但还是能看下来，等于复习党史，很好</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1226440987", "nick_name": "Sundance小千", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/monster1000/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1564786-9.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2017-08-08", "content": "<span class=\"short\">小学时的午睡读物，谭甫仁遇刺一章印象最深刻</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "259840452", "nick_name": "荒箬", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/huangruo/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1352740-45.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2010-06-12", "content": "<span class=\"short\">为当权者讳 有失公允 </span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "590441532", "nick_name": "小小虫", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/xiaoxiaochonglt/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u23237106-11.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2012-10-12", "content": "<span class=\"short\">想当年每个假期都会看个大部头，现在更得更不务正业了……</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "247912161", "nick_name": "北纬41度", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/31818291/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u31818291-18.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2010-05-06", "content": "<span class=\"short\">我也不知道我看过多少遍的书了</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1022603520", "nick_name": "海右风歌", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/34657548/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u34657548-7.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-03-18", "content": "<span class=\"short\">话说这套书我还真看过，文笔虽然一般，但思路还是很清晰的，对一些历史也没有回避。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "870371996", "nick_name": "大道隐于市", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/63530235/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63530235-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2014-12-10", "content": "<span class=\"short\">最近发生了这么多事情，需要置于一个共和国历史下思考其意义，忽然就想起了这本书，高中时候读的地摊货，津津有味，后来上了学术的贼船，不屑于这种野史了，现在的世道变幻，让我对这种成王败寇，英雄逐鹿的演义体笔法，又有了敬畏，有时候故事更加真实。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "545901861", "nick_name": "Flying", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/flyingvan/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43827212-6.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2012-06-19", "content": "<span class=\"short\">惊讶于那个年代就有这么客观，不顾政治阻力的小说，个人认为很客观的一本书呀！</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "734227112", "nick_name": "绿茶生活", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2029274/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2029274-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2013-10-10", "content": "<span class=\"short\">这套书，最值得读的应该是中册，因为那段历史，我们都零七碎八地知道，但按时间轴排在一起的，这还是我看到的第一本书。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "920598016", "nick_name": "肱二蜀黍", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1556625/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1556625-36.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2017-07-23", "content": "<span class=\"short\">了解当时的历史细节，还是值得一读的。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "834843831", "nick_name": "SoYoung", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/soyoung1986/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44467908-21.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2014-08-10", "content": "<span class=\"short\">前段时期和朋友提到过，就突然想起来这也属于流散在小时候读过而又一时遗忘的书籍海洋里了。那个时期看到这本书，便对文革那段历史十分感兴趣，而囿于年纪，无法理解，只知道那是个很纠结的年代。对所有人来说都很纠结并影响深远的年代，包括我们，甚至包括我们的下一代。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "54389568", "nick_name": "leonson", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/leonson/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1106146-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2008-08-14", "content": "<span class=\"short\">已经难能可贵了</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "525025024", "nick_name": "GRANDEUR", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/zl900901/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47587727-15.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2012-04-27", "content": "<span class=\"short\">当年深爱这本书，可惜后半段让爸爸借出去了。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "853984392", "nick_name": "陈安白", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/50318763/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50318763-6.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2014-10-14", "content": "<span class=\"short\">回家仔细看书架时，才想起自己中学时居然还看完了三本一套的这种题材的书。真不可思议。。。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "515172251", "nick_name": "地中有山", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/shenhuiqian/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u38672080-11.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">不好，跟政治课本差不多。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1220239005", "nick_name": "whj", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2012440/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2012440-137.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-07-26", "content": "<span class=\"short\">只记得周总理的初恋女友了…</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1254368158", "nick_name": "超天大圣孙悟空", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/149081061/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u149081061-322.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2017-10-09", "content": "<span class=\"short\">其实读着还挺有意思的</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1142690488", "nick_name": "南渡", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/zswxlong/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u76793200-126.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2017-01-27", "content": "<span class=\"short\">3.5在爷爷的书架再见此书，培养了我对政治的某种趣味</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "26418013", "nick_name": "风漏菜籽", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/jxsdxiao/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1871469-5.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">中华人民共和国演义</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1188483050", "nick_name": "金灯道君", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/136741175/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u136741175-45.jpg", "use_num": "1", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-05-10", "content": "<span class=\"short\">说是小说，但其本质不过是三流的纪实文学。无论毛主席，周总理，还是彭大将军在这书里的言谈举止，都透露着一股子小文人的酸味，哪有半点一代枭雄的魄力？要不是为了了解这段历史，我才看不下去这玩意儿。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "663442027", "nick_name": "不屑帝", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/56539741/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56539741-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2013-04-05", "content": "<span class=\"short\">非常好的书 小学时候看这么好的书真幸运 通过这本书的客观描写让我心中过去伟大无比的毛泽东同志走下神坛 看东西尽量全面要客观 要自己擦亮自己的眼睛！</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "276257713", "nick_name": "[已注销]", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/sniper3547/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2010-07-29", "content": "<span class=\"short\">很长</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "15185910", "nick_name": "yangtou", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1589099/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2007-06-04", "content": "<span class=\"short\">小时候看过，好多八卦。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "23455081", "nick_name": "龙青", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1570316/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1570316-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2007-11-08", "content": "<span class=\"short\">比较客观地展现了历史的本来面目，也有一些不为人知的细节。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1331598479", "nick_name": "kostoglotov", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/kostoglotov/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u167767601-15.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2018-02-25", "content": "<span class=\"short\">应该是五年级时候看的书，算是二十世纪历史启蒙读物了。记得当年看完三本之后还去看了党史？当年怎么心这么大？</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "408840391", "nick_name": "circlestar", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/circlestar/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2011-07-01", "content": "<span class=\"short\">大的事件和人物关系符合历史，对过程有艺术化加工，正是董哲所谓的“大事不虚，小事不拘”。但由于把这么长一段时期放在一起用三本书写，很难展开。很多大事由于各种原因没提到或一带而过，但能看出，作者对史料的掌握还是比较好的，对章节、情节的编排也下了很多功夫。对于需要粗略了解中国近几十年历史脉络的人来说可以看，对近现代史有一定了解的人不必看。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "226496665", "nick_name": "lorenzo", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/36091264/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36091264-6.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar10 rating", "comment_time": "2010-03-08", "content": "<span class=\"short\">rt，不知道在写些什么，对于历史的简单记叙？又多了些多余的对话和虚构情节，一部历史小说：那里说了？都在苍白地记叙，全书重点不在写共和国的历史，而在如何才能不被领导人给屏蔽</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "984535792", "nick_name": "helmes", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/69689636/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u69689636-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2015-12-06", "content": "<span class=\"short\">枯燥的共和国历史入门读物</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "379974457", "nick_name": ">>Smileˋ波", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/50961774/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2011-04-18", "content": "<span class=\"short\">知道了那段历史</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "24987449", "nick_name": "jake", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2049698/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2007-11-30", "content": "<span class=\"short\">讲述清王朝推翻民国建立，直到中华人民共和国成立。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1029223344", "nick_name": "[已注销]", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/candycrusher/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-04-07", "content": "<span class=\"short\">这本书的中心思想可以概括为：江青、康生、姚文元万恶、林彪九恶、毛泽东七善三恶、刘邓周千古完人，尽善尽美。一切罪责归四人帮、林彪。一切功劳归刘邓周。描写有关四人帮的情节时加油添醋、极尽丑化之能事。态度极不中立、客观。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1026027816", "nick_name": "Allope", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/70847081/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u70847081-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2016-03-29", "content": "<span class=\"short\">一部三本，从初中开始看了无数遍，对领导人的刻画很细腻，对文革描写的很详细。总体来看，极好。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "870853118", "nick_name": "红砖块", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/107490683/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u107490683-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2014-12-12", "content": "<span class=\"short\">我应该是初三的时候看的这本书，也不记得当时是怎么知道的这本书。只记得从图书馆借的时候遮遮掩掩的，觉得是本禁书。但读起来很有趣味，也比较客观， 事件描述也很完整，时间跨度也很大，是一本不错的通俗历史读物。</span>\n            "}], "reviews": [{"review_id": "6704140", "review_title": "演绎历史", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/73382842/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "nick_name": "taodachong", "review_score": "allstar30 main-title-rating", "review_time": "2014-06-16 21:37:22", "review_content": "<div class=\"main-bd\">\n\n\n    \n  \n    \n\n    <div id=\"link-report\">\n      <div class=\"review-content clearfix\" data-author=\"taodachong\" data-url=\"https://book.douban.com/review/6704140/\" data-original=\"0\">\n        早年去中央编译局实习，师傅就说，什么最虚？历史。什么最真？故事。你要认真就干不好这工作。不是个认真的人，却较上了真，于是被赶回来开了小吃摊，过起了和城管打游击的战斗岁月。<br><br>既然故事最真，演义就比传记更靠谱，貂蝉说不准真的被关羽收编，关羽说不准真有个生活秘书叫周仓，这都不好说。<br><br>近些年总有些人受到了中国式的教育，思想变得极为critical，遇事即喷，他却反过来教训中国教育体制，说禁锢了思想，谁谁如果稍有不认可他的意见，便祭起大旗，说人被洗脑，其实如果脑子真的那么容易洗，我早就不卖小吃，开干洗店了，专门洗脑。<br><br>人家打出招牌叫演义，你非要去抠他字眼，说白崇禧是个gay，怎么可能死在女人肚皮上？说彪哥也没那么英明神武，坏事的也未见得都是他老婆孩。这么认真干啥？隋唐演义动辄梦游天外，东周列国说缪毐小弟弟像车轮一样粗，从古到今几人急过？<br><br>所谓演义比正史更真实，不是说D史就不客观，当然不客观是很客观的评价，而是说演义有时更符合逻辑，更让人容易接受，接受的多了，没有的也可能就有了，比如周仓，关平以及杨再兴。<br><br>时间机器发明出来之前，你就信演义的又如何？太祖熟读三国因之权谋无双，他读的可是三国演义，没听说他读的是三国志。<br><br>鉴于今天世界杯来店里吃烧烤的人实在较多，要忙于生意。就收尾吧。因此，所以，这书还是不错的，有一定借鉴意义，尤其是对权谋场上的同志，然而，又是不够的，因为它毕竟是演义。\n      </div>\n\n      \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"main-author\">\n      \n  \n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n      \n  ", "use_num": "\n      有用 6\n  ", "nouse_num": "\n      没用 1\n  ", "review_share": "", "review_reward": "", "review_comments": []}]}